{"tid":1631940,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"CityU 會停幾日課？你地點平衡學業同出街？","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:40:01.000Z","uid":244653,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03f38b7bdd904f5b66306fb0e1323b2f711fb7d1","tid":1631940,"uid":244653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:47.000Z","msg":"下個星期有presentation ，我星期五發夢個腦都成日迎住整powerpoint<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，cityu到底會停幾日？"},{"pid":"40cf23d8ffbd6b0963d9c7ac86caed051ad05027","tid":1631940,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"3dde6890582ef0cb6c23bb36b4f2e0f2ef8d0940","tid":1631940,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:55.000Z","msg":"BBC:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLwxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=319dc2fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&h=20132a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548</a><br />\nAnti-government marches in Hong Kong have ended in rioting, with attacks on government offices, a metro station and businesses with ties to mainland China.<br />\n<br />\nCNN:<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLwxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=8167c44e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence%2F&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsLwxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=d8626d9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6HkAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm6HkAU.jpg&h=cfadcc90&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNQQuuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNQQuuf.jpg&h=e8fe24d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkz2kAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdkz2kAV.jpg&h=e42958dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wt3FRHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWt3FRHB.jpg&h=836cc635&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n開始無人話警察武力不對等，國際開始支持港府。再係咁落去，美國人權及民主法案好可能被否決<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以做多D外國文宣 (Twitter), 唔好覺得有班人會做, 人人都要文宣!!"},{"pid":"c9956738cb3f3f73e74934a187fc55082043b9ca","tid":1631940,"uid":301906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"如果狗鐵呢幾日都關站嘅話可能會繼續停掛我估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53981640dee3b703854a1a83e0eff43205797251","tid":1631940,"uid":147916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c9956738cb3f3f73e74934a187fc55082043b9ca","tid":1631940,"uid":301906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"如果狗鐵呢幾日都關站嘅話可能會繼續停掛我估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:01:21.000Z","msg":"希望九龍塘唔會咁快開啦<br />\n仲有份report未做好呀屌"},{"pid":"e8e2bd2e00ac66146ac8f622df7694d060411d42","tid":1631940,"uid":315502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"cityu有冇巴絲tg gp/行動gp？"},{"pid":"d8c84